author: Christal Hayes
title: Amphitheater at Lake Eola spray painted with profanity
text:
Christal Hayes . Christal Hayes / Orlando Sentinel Vandals spray painted "F*** Buddy Lies" on the stage at the Walt Disney Amphitheater at Lake Eola over the weekend. Vandals spray painted "F*** Buddy Lies" on the stage at the Walt Disney Amphitheater at Lake Eola over the weekend. (Christal Hayes / Orlando Sentinel) Christal Hayes / Orlando Sentinel Vandals spray painted "F*** Buddy Lies" on the stage at the Walt Disney Amphitheater at Lake Eola over the weekend. Vandals spray painted "F*** Buddy Lies" on the stage at the Walt Disney Amphitheater at Lake Eola over the weekend. (Christal Hayes / Orlando Sentinel) 
Orlando police are investigating the incident and say there are a number of cameras in the area that may have captured whoever defaced the area. 
Orlando Lt. Tom Woodhall said it was unclear what or who the graffiti was directed toward or why it was done. 
It appears some of the spray paint had been scrubbed off by Sunday evening but some of the green and red paint still left the stage stained. 
Anyone with information in this incident can call Crimeline at 800-423-8477.
